items.name: POV Ass Grab
items.description:
This is a LoRA for POV Ass Grab.

I suggest using this LoRA at 0.6-1.0 weight for best results.

  • Use CLIP SKIP 2.

  • This was trained on NAI. NAI-based models will give the best results.

  • Tested on AOM2 (Worked), AOM3 A1 (Worked), 7th Anime (Worked), Pastel Mix (Worked), My Own Mix (Worked), Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix (Worked), Chillout Mix (Kinda Worked), Dreamshaper (Doesn't Work).

  • Always add this to the prompt with the LoRA to activate it properly: povag, pov hands, ass grab

  • Add the tags: pussy, spread pussy to spread her pussy.

  • Add the tags: lying, on stomach - To make her lay down.

  • Add the tag: from below to grab her ass from below.

  • Just adding pussy, anus gives slightly different results.

  • Try other other descriptive tags - It might give you interesting results.

Known Issues

  • If it has issues with character LoRAs, try lowering the character's weight - This is how I fixed it.

  • If it's changing the style too much - Just lower the weight of the Ass Grab LoRA to 0.6-0.7 to fix it. It's slightly overbaked.

  • If you don't describe anything (hairstyle, hair color, clothing) and only have base tags - It will only generate her ass and nothing else sometimes.

  • Sometimes her ass will fuse with panties or clothing when using pussy, anus, or spread pussy tags. You can add bottomless or cameltoe to fix this.

  • Anus, Spread Anus - doesn't work too well compared to Pussy, Spread Pussy tags.

  • If you have issues with the eyes - Upscale or add looking back, looking at viewer to help the AI generate them better.

  • This is only V1 - It will have it's issues but will be updated in the future with V2.

Embeds and LoRAs used

Everything I'm making will always be free but if you want to show a little bit more support, you can buy me a coffee - https://ko-fi.com/ekune

items.name: Black Sclera | Feature
items.description:
Training on "black sclera".

I have been working to integrate various unique features into LoRa's (and now LoCon). I have found making individual trainings on each feature, then merging the ones needed together gets remarkable results.

Eyes are hard to get right, this helps but isn't a perfect solution yet though.

This has been trained on about 80 AI generated images from various models (picked out from hundreds), after using a couple not so great lora's I had experimented with before.

This can be used stand-alone to add black sclera with much higher efficiency, or mixed with other LoRA / LoCon to mix the feature in. I recommend to avoid using this with multiple other LoRA / LoCon without mixing first, it is more prone to cause issues.

If you like this, get me a coffee :D

items.name: Assaultron - Fallout
items.description:
RobCo™ has done it again with their latest in engineering: The Assaultron!

This is a lora trained on 136 hand picked images of assaultrons from the Fallout series. There are no 3d/sfm images included, it's exclusively digital art. It gets the 'face' and single eye pretty well, and can do the claw-arms too... sometimes. It was trained on danbooru-style tags, so use those when trying to prompt - I've included the tags in a .txt file in the "Training Images" download below.

It works pretty well with most ckpts, but I recommend Anything 4.5, I used it for all of the example images.

NOTES:

-Most assaultrons trained in this lora were green, but there were a good amount of blue ones too (Ada). You can change the color of the robot by emphasizing tags like: blue_armor, blue_skin, etc ...or use other colors. See example images.

-Unlike other models I've made, this one can't really do a "male version" assaultron, but you're welcome to go and try.

-The claw arms are the most inconsistent part of this, sometimes it will get confused on whether to do a normal hand or the three claw bits.

This lora: https://civitai.com/models/4885/itrobo2022-highly-detailed-robots compliments this one pretty well. Makes the robot look more robotic.

Example prompt: (See example images, most images still have their metadata. Just drag the images onto the PNG info tab and import it.)

items.description:
Please check the AHS character guidelines regarding the use of characters. https://www.ah-soft.com/character/index.html

Study at ACertainty.ckpt. Recommended strength is about 0.4 to 0.6.

The reproducible costume is only the jam band version

Costume reproduction requires a lot of prompts.

example: blonde very long hair, antenna hair, headphones, hair ornament, green eyes, red necktie, bare shoulders, detached sleeves, cleavage, red skirt, single thighhigh,

It seems that the reproducibility is higher if the torso part of the costume is not specified, but it also feels a little vague.

The learning material does not have a background, so if you want a background, please specify it strongly in the prompt.

If the reproducibility of this LoRA is increased, the versatility will decrease, making it difficult to pose and compose. Please use ControlNet etc.

キャラクターの利用に関しては、AHSキャラクターのガイドラインを確認してください。https://www.ah-soft.com/charactor/index.html

ACertainty.ckptにて学習。強度は0.4～0.6くらいを推奨。

再現可能な衣装はjamバンド版のみです

衣装の再現には多くのプロンプトが必要です。

例：blonde very long hair, antenna hair, headphones, hair ornament, green eyes, red necktie, bare shoulders, detached sleeves, cleavage, red skirt, single thighhigh,

衣装の胴部分は下手に指定をしない方が再現率は高いようですが、ややあやふやな感じもします。各自で調節してください。

学習素材に背景がないので、背景が必要な場合はプロンプトで強めに指定してください。

このLoRAは再現性を高めると汎用性が低くなり、ポーズや構図がつけにくいです。ControlNetなどを活用してください。

items.name: Chinese Stealth Suit - Fallout
items.description:
Chinese stealth armor, also known as Hēi Guǐ is a set of armor from Fallout 3, and the subsequent games. I really liked this armor and decided to train a lora on it, despite there being VERY little art of this set online.

This is a lora trained on 32 hand picked images of the Chinese stealth suit from the Fallout series. There are a good amount of 3d renders in this, but the digital art was weighted heavily during training, so it can do digital and realistic pretty well. Despite trained on so few images compared to number of images I usually do, it gets the features really well, and seems to understand how the front and back look. It was trained on danbooru-style tags, so use those when trying to prompt - I've included the tags in a .txt file in the "Training Images" download below.

It works pretty well with most ckpts, but I recommend Anything 4.5, I used it for most of the example images.

NOTES:

-The helmet can be removed if you put "helmet, faceless" and similar tags in negatives, and also prompt what the characters face is supposed to look like. So this doubles down as just a stealth suit with no helmet if you want to try and put characters in it. See example image for a helmetless character.

-It was only trained on the "female" version of the armor, however it can generate male characters and body types in it quite well.

Example prompt: (See example images, all images should still have their metadata. Just drag the images onto the PNG info tab and import it.)

items.name: 阿尔泰尔 Altair(Re:Creators) Character Lora
items.description:
这是我第一次制作Lora模型，这个模型还有很多问题，非常抱歉。

————23.3.20————

V2.0更新了什么：

这次我使用了768x768的数据集进行训练。

增加了更多的Trigger Words，现在可以生成Q版的阿尔泰尔，以及动画中阿尔泰尔在占据席利乌斯的身体后的最终形态，还有裸体围裙（实际上还有其他的服饰，但是生成相对有些困难）的阿尔泰尔以及不带帽子的阿尔泰尔

测试了anyhentai，kotosmix以及AbyssOrangeMix2，在这几个模型上运行的相对不错，其他模型我并未尝试，如果可以的话，希望有人可以尝试使用其他的模型（包括真人模型）进行生成，并把结果发布在评论区。

请注意，这个版本的部分关键词是用于生成不同风格和不同服饰的阿尔泰尔的，因此部分关键词可能存在冲突。

如果生成的人物图像面部不佳，推荐您勾选高清修复。

在使用关键词final-form时可能会导致人物面部出现问题。

部分情况下画面会偏向于蓝色，未来我会调整数据集并重新训练模型。

细节上，整体而言相对于V1.0更好，但是部分情况下可能仍然会出现问题。

————————

这个Lora模型是基于final-prune.ckpt（【旧短哈希1d4a34af】新短哈希22fa233c2d）训练出的。

使用的是512x640的数据集，大多数图片来自danbooru，少部分来自rule34，以及我个人使用mikumikudance的阿尔泰尔模型截图得到的图片。

这个模型可以生成nsfw的图片。

这个模型在生成真人的效果上非常糟糕，而且用它生成的人物的眼睛会有不少问题，另外在使用部分2d模型时画面可能会比较模糊，必须勾选高清修复，才能得到比较好的效果，可能是在训练时我没有设置好，导致模型过拟合了。

在高分辨率的情况下可能会出现奇怪的问题。

推荐使用0.6-0.8的权重，除了提到的触发词以外，其他的人物特征是不必要提到的，但如果你想要更好的效果，也可以添加，因为一些细节（比如人物的袖章，或者护手可能会在生成时丢失）。

通常altair和1girl这两个触发词是必须的。

如果你想得到我展示的一部分图片的效果，请使用AbyssOrangeMix2或者AbyssOrangeMix3，还有Perfect World以及anyhentai这些模型中的一个，并使用orangemix.vae，这个vae的下载链接可以在AbyssOrangeMix2 - Hardcore的下载页面找到。

然后，设置40steps，7CFG Scale，采样方法(Sampler)选择DPM++2M Karras，或者其他DPM++ Karras的采样方法，下方的Lora权重设置为0.75，想要更好的效果可以勾选面部修复以及高清修复，但高清修复可能会导致生成一些人体结构奇怪的图片。

推荐使用512x640的分辨率。

近期可能还会对这个模型进行改进，直到它令我满意为止。

我很喜欢Re:Creators里面的这个白色拖把精（阿尔泰尔），但是civitai上没有她的lora，所以只能自己训练它了。

英语是用Google翻译翻译的，如果有造成误解之处非常抱歉。

This is the first time I make a Lora model, there are still many problems with this model, I am very sorry.

——— 23.3.20————

What's updated in V2.0:

This time I used a 768x768 dataset for training.

Added more Trigger Words, now you can generate the Q version of Altair, and the final form of Altair in the animation after occupying the body of Silius, and the naked apron (actually there are other costumes, but generated Relatively difficult) Altair and Altair without hat

I have tested anyhentai, kotosmix and AbyssOrangeMix2, and they work relatively well on these models. I have not tried other models. If possible, I hope someone can try to use other models (including real-life models) to generate and publish the results. in the comments section.

Please note that some keywords in this version are used to generate Altairs with different styles and different clothing, so some keywords may conflict.

If the face of the generated character image is not good, it is recommended that you check HD Repair.

When using the keyword final-form, it may cause problems with the character's face.

In some cases, the picture will be biased towards blue. In the future, I will adjust the data set and retrain the model.

In terms of details, overall it is better than V1.0, but there may still be problems in some cases.

———————

This Lora model is trained based on final-prune.ckpt ([old short hash 1d4a34af] new short hash 22fa233c2d).

The data set of 512x640 is used, most of the pictures are from danbooru, a small part is from rule34, and I personally use the pictures obtained from the screenshot of the Altair model of mikumikudance.

This model can generate pictures of nsfw.

This model is very bad at generating real people, and the eyes of the characters generated with it will have many problems. In addition, when using some 2D models, the picture may be blurry. You must check HD repair to get better results. , it may be that I did not set it properly during training, which caused the model to overfit.

Strange issues can occur at high resolutions.

It is recommended to use a weight of 0.6-0.8. Except for the trigger words mentioned, other character characteristics are not necessary to mention, but if you want better results, you can also add them, because some details (such as the character's armband, Or the gauntlet might be missing on spawn).

Usually the two trigger words altair and 1girl are required.

If you want to get the effect of some of the pictures I show, please use AbyssOrangeMix2 or AbyssOrangeMix3, and one of the models Perfect World and anyhentai, and use orangemix.vae, the download link of this vae can be found on the download page of AbyssOrangeMix2 - Hardcore.

Then, set 40steps, 7CFG Scale, sampling method (Sampler) to select DPM++2M Karras, or other sampling methods of DPM++ Karras, and set the Lora weight below to 0.75. If you want a better effect, you can check the face repair and high-definition repair , but the high-definition restoration may result in some strange images of human anatomy.

A resolution of 512x640 is recommended.

This model may be improved in the near future until it satisfies me.

I really like the white mop spirit (Altair) in Re:Creators, but there is no her lora on civitai, so I can only train it myself.

English is translated by Google Translate, sorry if there is any misunderstanding.

items.name: EastAsianDollLikeness
items.description:
This is my first Lora, please be nice and forgiving for any mishaps.

EastAsiaDollLikeness_V5

What's difference ?

Main difference within korean, Japanese, Taiwan Doll Likeness is this one produces a East Asian baby faces or round faces.

Inspired by Doll Likeness created by various masters, I wanted to make a beautiful East Asian face. Since I have a soft spot for cute types such as baby faces and East Asian round faces, So I decided to make a Lora to mimic this face shape.

Having tried 3 versions before, all were unsatisfactory, and this model is by no means perfect, but it certainly has something that I find very attractive.

Please try and share and reply your results or give suggestions.

In the future, I will continue to try to make a better Lora.

support me on my patreon, help me upgrade Hardware for trainning and testing more models. Or buy me a coffee. thanks~

Tips:

• It is recommended to use (oval face) in the prompt, the effect of pinching the face of Lora will be better, and it will not produce a baby fat face.

• Also works great with other Doll Likenesses like Korean or Japanese.

• This model works best in ChilloutMix

For V5:

• The best result of using this Lora alone is around 0.4~0.85. Below 0.4 it is easy to become a mixed race or a foreign face (you can also try it if you prefer mixed race).

For V4:

• The best result of using this Lora alone is around 0.7~1.0. Below 0.6 it is easy to become a mixed race or a foreign face (you can also try it if you prefer mixed race).

Disclaimer:

As the author, I regret to inform you that the LORA model is not intended for commercial use. This decision has been made in order to prevent any potential controversies or legal issues related to impersonation or defamation that may arise from the use of the model for commercial purposes. Furthermore, allowing commercial use of the model may have a negative impact on the development of the AI community. Therefore, I strongly advise against any commercial usage of the LORA model.

The second character illustrated by Samail, AUG appears to be a slim doll around 160cm tall. Just like the previous T-Doll drawn by Samail RF Kar98k, the gun itself looks slightly oversized when compared to the doll, but the scale ratio is a lot better; the proportion is relatively sound, and thus comparisons can be made using the weapon as a scale comparison.

AUG has long bleached blonde hair, tightened up to the side by a large flower ribbon. She can be identified by her beauty mark below her right eye and her golden-coloured pupils. Her outfit itself is dark themed, similar to some of the YoRHa issue android combat uniforms from NieR:Automata.
